
Welcome to this Wiki.  It is a VimWiki.

This is the Start page.

Add this to your ~/.vimrc

:noremap gf :e <cfile><cr>

Use gf on a word to open up a file with that name.

Use <CTRL>-o to go back to the previous file.

There are multiple WikiSpaces here in subdirectories.

Use <F5> to change to the current directory of the page you are on.

nmap <F5> :lcd%:p:h<CR>:pwd<CR>

